{"tid":1838550,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"世衛： 感謝 習近平 領導應對與防範疫情","createTime":"2020-01-24T05:17:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T07:53:01.000Z","uid":226548,"like":26,"dislike":324,"uniUserReply":127,"replies":[{"pid":"a275930a2ff87d08720c9383bc99696ad414e73a","tid":1838550,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:17:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/24115624/image1579838168401.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F24115624%2Fimage1579838168401.png&h=f8ffb691&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n世界衛生組織在日內瓦召開兩日緊急會議後，決定暫不將武漢新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情列為國際關注的突發公共衛生事件，認為將疫情界定為國際公共衛生事件言之尚早。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞昨日提到，世衛現時有團隊在中國調查。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">他感謝中國國家衛生健康委員會合作，以及中國國家主席習近平領導應對與防範疫情。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n中國當局最新公布，全國現有830宗確診病例，其中177宗重症，26宗死亡。<br />\n<br />\n（圖片來源：World Health Organization (WHO) YouTube影片截圖）"},{"pid":"5c492e76cc7611f0915f0a1ceb06dfd71435bdc8","tid":1838550,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:18:06.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/295842/【武漢肺炎】世衛未列武漢肺炎為國際公共衛生事/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F295842%2F%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9B%E6%9C%AA%E5%88%97%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E7%82%BA%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%A1%9B%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%8B%2F&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=f07097d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/295842/【武漢肺炎】世衛未列武漢肺炎為國際公共衛生事/</a>"},{"pid":"f6618e30735ecf574739e1a5761bb2bd629a71eb","tid":1838550,"uid":39167,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:18:48.000Z","msg":"CHO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6e4f52779df1d0e8e7f9f903ef3f464213cb34","tid":1838550,"uid":78304,"like"