ji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab1a2cec1336da4c5b147d5bf526678b3970b2b","tid":1838550,"uid":103916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:57:40.000Z","msg":"屌⋯⋯佢已經呢埋落屎坑到啦。<br />\n已經冇人搵到佢。"},{"pid":"246cd167cef6adc13f8a7f08ea6e6572475ed2f4","tid":1838550,"uid":55497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:58:17.000Z","msg":"好撚嘢 習近平"},{"pid":"bba605d113f6968fd5d0448a480c9eb55fb3632a","tid":1838550,"uid":278649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:58:39.000Z","msg":"支那衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90017319942bfdca5b6d70092b5344eb6c9cd138","tid":1838550,"uid":25183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7c6ce0484f74d8b28bccfb458ff2c375c4263243","tid":1838550,"uid":127791,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0cfd41ac48e0cb48fcd687b499133fddc6240267","tid":1838550,"uid":277186,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:20:36.000Z","msg":"依個黑鬼係咪d非洲窮閪國家既人?"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:30:17.000Z","msg":"津巴布韋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:59:01.000Z","msg":"屌，明白晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cce614241492c9be457cc4723f647618a0370e9","tid":1838550,"uid":337714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:00:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5178dd136a6a2cd46796117a26806a64343f35b","tid":1838550,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:02:40.000Z","msg":"有冇醫學專家屌鳩呢個總幹事"},{"pid":"a4c7037e50675c3290f32173ba9f1c62d42f9f4a","tid":1838550,"uid":11328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:04:04.000Z","ms